channel.title: [Release] CB Brace [Release] ~ [Showoff] Ice Cream [Showoff]
channel.description:
Yet another night of being bored so I decided to make my own version of a combat bracelet and an ice-cream :P (yum!)
I will show the ice-cream first then the bracelet and then the download.
Please give feed back and also give me suggestions on new models to make and how I could improve things.
The Ice-Cream [IMG]http://i546.photobucket.com/albums/hh417/Runescapecomunity/3dicecream2.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i546.photobucket.com/albums/hh417/Runescapecomunity/3dicecream1.jpg[/img]
The Combat Bracelet [IMG]http://i546.photobucket.com/albums/hh417/Runescapecomunity/cbbrace1.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i546.photobucket.com/albums/hh417/Runescapecomunity/cbbrace2.jpg[/img]
Download the bracelet [url=http://dfcf4725.linkbucks.com]here.[/url]
I will make ints if people need them.
